               <p>659. 
               
                  <persName id="t17930911-112-defend1174" type="defendantName">
                     JOHN 
                     THOMPSON
                  <interp inst="t17930911-112-defend1174" type="surname" value="THOMPSON"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17930911-112-defend1174" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17930911-112-defend1174" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17930911-112-defend1174" type="age" value="41"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
             was indicted for that <rs id="t17930911-112-off606" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17930911-112-off606" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17930911-112-off606" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>
               he on the <rs id="t17930911-112-cd607" type="crimeDate">16th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17930911-112-off606 t17930911-112-cd607"></join>, feloniously did forge, falsly make and counterfeit a certain receipt for money, bearing date the 16th of April, purporting to be the receipt of one 
                     <persName id="t17930911-112-person1175">
                        Edward
                         Howis
                     <interp inst="t17930911-112-person1175" type="surname" value="Howis"></interp>
