                        <interp inst="t17930911-112-person1175" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                   and Co. whereby the said 
                     <persName id="t17930911-112-person1176">
                        Edward
                         Howis
                     <interp inst="t17930911-112-person1176" type="surname" value="Howis"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17930911-112-person1176" type="given" value="Edward"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17930911-112-person1176" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                   did acknowledge to receive of the Honourable St. John, the sum of 16 l. with intent to defraud 
                     
                        <persName id="t17930911-112-victim1178" type="victimName">
                           Edward 
                           Howis
                        <interp inst="t17930911-112-victim1178" type="surname" value="Howis"></interp>
